<img src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/Jamie-Chang-b.jpg" alt width="150" height="150" border="1" />
<br/>
<div class="phototagleft">
</div>
</div>
<p style="border:none; padding:0in"><strong>Jamie Chang&nbsp;</strong>is a literary translator. Her translation of&nbsp;Kim Jiyoung, Born 1982&nbsp;was longlisted for the 2020 National Book Awards in Translated Literature. She is the recipient of the Daesan Foundation Translation Grant and a three-time recipient of the Literature Translation Institute of Korea Grant.</p>
<div class="clear"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
